dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures, soundings, and spot heights. At head of title: Azores. Includes 6 cross sections and 6 insets: Caldeira of Graciosa -- [Gomez Bay] -- Praya de Graciosa -- Angra de Terceira -- Praya de Terceira -- [Cabras Islands]. "1818." "Published according to Act of Parliament at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty, July 23rd, 1849." North oriented to the upper left.
dc_creator_sm: Vidal, A. T. E. (Alexander Thomas Emeric), 1792-1863
dc_publisher_s: London : Published ... at the Hydrographic Office of the Admiralty ; sold by R.B. Bate, agent for the sale of the Admiralty charts, 21 Poultry, 1849.
